    DINNER

    Experience refined Greek dining at Meli Estiatorio in Forest Hills, NY. Our dinner menu features a selection of fresh, seasonal Mediterranean dishes, including whole grilled fish, succulent lamb chops, and pan-seared sesame-crusted feta. Complement your meal with house-made pastas, such as tagliatelle with rock shrimp and lobster linguine.
